5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

caret-sheet

Generic function

Summary

Returns the sheet that owns the specified caret.

Signature

cursor-sheet caret => sheet

Arguments

caret
An instance of type <caret>.

Values

sheet
An instance of type <sheet>.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns the sheet that owns caret.

See also

caret-position, page 216

caret-size, page 217
